        "text": "The declaration must conform to the standardized wording provided for in Section 211; see Notes to Boxes Nos. VIII, VIII (i) to (v) (in general) and the specific Notes to Box No.VIII (i). If this Box is not used, this sheet should not be included in the request.\nDeclaration as to the identity of the inventor (Rules 4.17(i) and 51bis.1(a)(i)):\nForm PCT/RO/101 (declaration sheet (i)) (March 2001; reprint July 2003)",
